lead_paragraph: The Journal of Commerce, only a few days since, tried to anticipate the action of the Anti-Rent State Convention. It took it for granted the Anti-Renters would make up a ticket to suit their own ends ; that they would select from both the other tickets the men supposed to be favorable to their views, and: put them in nomination.
